                     <interp inst="t18760918-445-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>, Stealing a gelding, a cart, and a set of harness, of <persName id="t18760918-name-367" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18760918-name-367" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18760918-name-367" type="surname" value="BENNETT"></interp>
